#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.3"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.3:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Mettāvagga"
msgstr "1. Love"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 3. Paṭhamaappiyasutta → paṭhamapiyasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an8.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Paṭhamaappiyasutta"
msgstr "3. Disliked (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an8.3:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Aṭṭhahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu sabrahmacārīnaṃ appiyo ca "
"hoti amanāpo ca agaru ca abhāvanīyo ca."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, a mendicant with eight qualities is disliked and disapproved by "
"their spiritual companions, not respected or admired."

msgctxt "an8.3:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi aṭṭhahi?"
msgstr "What eight?"

msgctxt "an8.3:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu appiyapasaṃsī ca hoti, piyagarahī ca, lābhakāmo ca, "
"sakkārakāmo ca, ahiriko ca, anottappī ca, pāpiccho ca, micchādiṭṭhi ca."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant praises the disliked and criticizes the liked. They "
"desire material possessions and honor. They lack conscience and prudence. "
"They have wicked desires and wrong view."

msgctxt "an8.3:1.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭhahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu sabrahmacārīnaṃ "
"appiyo ca hoti amanāpo ca agaru ca abhāvanīyo ca."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant with these eight qualities is disliked and disapproved by their "
"spiritual companions, not respected or admired."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.156"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an8.3:2.1"
msgid ""
"Aṭṭhahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu sabrahmacārīnaṃ piyo ca "
"hoti manāpo ca garu ca bhāvanīyo ca."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant with eight qualities is liked and approved by their spiritual "
"companions, and respected and admired."

msgctxt "an8.3:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi aṭṭhahi?"
msgstr "What eight?"

msgctxt "an8.3:2.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na appiyapasaṃsī ca hoti, na piyagarahī ca, na "
"lābhakāmo ca, na sakkārakāmo ca, hirīmā ca hoti, ottappī ca, appiccho ca, "
"sammādiṭṭhi ca."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant doesn’t praise the disliked and criticize the liked. "
"They don’t desire material possessions and honor. They have conscience and "
"prudence. They have few desires and right view."

msgctxt "an8.3:2.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭhahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu sabrahmacārīnaṃ "
"piyo ca hoti manāpo ca garu ca bhāvanīyo cā”ti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant with these eight qualities is liked and approved by their "
"spiritual companions, and respected and admired.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.3:2.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
